Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:04.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When Kaga-san and I were lost in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:08.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai happened to show up and help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:11.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai had come to the university's seminar house
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:14.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,for an overnight trip with the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:20.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We had somehow ended up near the seminar house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:25.65,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(310,311)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Blackout
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:29.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:32.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kokoro odoru tomerarenai no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:38.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naite waratte kimi to no kioku zutto wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:48.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hontou no jibun wa doko ni iru toka
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Otona ni narutte taihen de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:55.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ima wa wasurete mo ii kana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:58.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yoru ga matte iru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:02.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kokoro wo hazumase aeru toki wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hashagi mawareba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:09.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tsutaetai omoi ni ima
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:12.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kizuite shimaisou de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:16.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kako to mirai osorete ite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:20.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Karappo no mama ja ugeokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:26.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tanoshimeba it's all right hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:33.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana koto zenbu wasurete kimi to issho ni odori akaseba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:40.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Motto suteki na jibun ni nareru sonna ki ga suru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:46.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Owaranai Golden Time gyutto chikazuku kimi to no kyori wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:54.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tsukazu hanarezu mawari michi demo taisetsu ni shitai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:58.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:00.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:04.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was so worried about what might've happened to you and Kaga-san, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:06.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was relieved to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:08.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:11.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:13.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san, Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:17.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you went on the same trip with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It sounded like a rough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:24.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:28.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop worrying about Banri and Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was worried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:34.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I texted you and Kouko a few times, but you didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:36.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You texted Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:39.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I couldn't help worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:45.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sure Kaga-san must have been overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.52,Dialogue15,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(362,133)}{\i1}Yanagisawa Mitsuo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.52,Dialogue15,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(262,166)}{\i1}No subject{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.52,Dialogue15,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(245,208)}{\i1}An overnight trip?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.52,Dialogue15,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(241,240)}{\i1}You sure you'll be okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I've got class. I'm going to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Bye bye, 2D-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sure, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:59.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san did a lot of introspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She said she's done a lot of things to make you hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:06.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah... youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Chinami, don't you have class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nope! I'm free until this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:15.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hang out with us, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:16.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Mitsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How is that your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,K-Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It is my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:31.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't want my boyfriend speaking to other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you that talking is cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:41.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you that I'm not your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't want you to do things I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why are you not even hearing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Because I didn't ask for your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where are you speaking from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,M-my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That voice is coming from your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How does that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:04.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't care how mysterious creatures do what they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:11.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but keep your hands off Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's not a request. It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo isn't just my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I plan on marrying him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's been decided by fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:26.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, we live in a different world from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I insist you understand here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop it, Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,O-Oka Chinami...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What kind of name is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:45.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know what that's supposed to mean, but call yourself whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:49.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Live however you'd like. Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um, my foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:54.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But do it in a world that has nothing to do with ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:58.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't butt in, don't get in our way, and don't come near Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just wanted to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Next time, you won't get off so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo, you texted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:15.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:16.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Listen, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:17.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Chinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:22.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:27.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to talk to Kaga-san about thanking the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:29.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, did you really have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And do you really have to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you hiding your armpit sweat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:45.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You realize you went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You look like a toad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:50.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think I should wipe my sweat in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:02.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are y-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Don't ask me if I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:04.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:05.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Don't "but" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:07.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:08.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't ask me what I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't tell me I'm being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:14.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know I'm dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, I made a huge mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:20.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I made him hate me again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:25.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been doing the same thing for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I couldn't stop myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I couldn't turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After all, I'm an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:35.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:42.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You wanted to thank the people from the festival club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:44.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I texted Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:48.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought we could go see her during lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:51.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I told the student affairs office about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:02.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I said some weird organization had infiltrated the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:10.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The people who tried to recruit you have been causing problems at other schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:15.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They make you buy really expensive accessories and charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They even run pyramid schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:18.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad you got out safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is more than a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't you join our club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:35.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'd like to check it out before I decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:39.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, we'd be glad to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We didn't get too many new members this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The festival club usually practices in that ward assembly hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Make sure you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't forget, Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What brought that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I almost remembered something just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I brought the kids from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm the president, Koshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:20.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everyone calls him Kosshi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As long as you're here, why don't you jump in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We were just practicing our Awa dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:37.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I had no idea Awa dancing was so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:40.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, you looked like you were dancing the robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you joining the festival club, Tada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:47.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hmm... It seemed fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not confident enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:55.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Besides, I intend to join the same club as Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:57.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:02.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll win Mitsuo over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:07.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:14.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}As first year law students,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:16.22,Dialogue13,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(363,137)}{\i1}Is Chinami-chan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:16.22,Dialogue13,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(239,192)}{\i1}your girlfriend?{\i0} 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:16.22,Dialogue13,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(222,241)}{\i1}She's three-dimensional,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:16.22,Dialogue13,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(227,292)}{\i1}but she's cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:18.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}you'll spend the next four years studying law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.52,Dialogue14,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,68)}{\i1}Is Chinami-chan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.52,Dialogue14,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(347,114)}{\i1}your girlfriend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.52,Dialogue14,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(250,154)}{\i1}She's three-dimensional,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.52,Dialogue14,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(271,196)}{\i1}but she's cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.52,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(78,289)}She's not my girlfriend yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.52,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(68,318)}It'd be nice if it worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}While we call it the study of law,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}it actually encompasses a variety of studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:27.26,Dialogue12,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(122,133)}{\i1}She's more than just cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:27.26,Dialogue12,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(58,166)}{\i1}She's funny, has a good personality,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:27.26,Dialogue12,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(162,196)}{\i1}and she's smart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:27.26,Dialogue12,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(106,239)}{\i1}She's everything I want!!!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:28.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}For example, there is positive law, basic law, the philosophy of law,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}legal history, and comparative law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.20,Dialogue17,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(238,153)}{\i1}WHAT ARE YOU{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.20,Dialogue17,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(253,189)}{\i1}GOING TO DO{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.20,Dialogue17,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(201,227)}{\i1}ABOUT KAGA-SAN?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:35.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Fields of study are further subdivided within these categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.20,Dialogue16,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(140,99)}{\i1}Wasn't Kaga-san{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.20,Dialogue16,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(230,147)}{\i1}a childhood friend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}As you advance in your studies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:40.61,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(224,93)}KAGA-SAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:40.61,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(212,130)}IS IN LOVE WITH
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:40.61,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(269,171)}YANA-SAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:43.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}you will be required to choose a specialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:43.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Without becoming too attached to your specialization,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:49.92,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(156,230)}I'll make it clear to Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:49.92,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(183,266)}I'll make sure she understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:49.92,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(194,304)}I want a serious relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:49.92,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(203,338)}with Chinami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:49.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}we hope you will approach law with a broad perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:51.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Laws are the rules of society, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:01.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san didn't come to college once that week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:06.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even when I texted her, she only told me not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:04.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.77,Dialogue18,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(342,87)}{\i1}Kaga Kouko{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.77,Dialogue18,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(346,116)}{\i1}No subject{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.77,Dialogue17,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(288,157)}{\i1}Don't worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:11.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,On Saturday, Kaga-san invited me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:15.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You must have been lonely without any contact from me for four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I had to prepare for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I intend to settle things once and for all today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:26.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Listen, should I really be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're our witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:33.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm about to prove that Mitsuo and I should be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we need you to stick around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why is the mood so combative?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,First, our birthplaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.87,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(100,219)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaga Household
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.87,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(283,348)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yanagisawa Household
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is the Kaga household.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:47.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is the Yanagisawa household.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:51.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're 800 meters apart and in the same school district.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:56.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if we had attended public school, it was highly likely we would meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In other words, it was inevitable that we would meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is a picture of our field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The sports festival, camp school, graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're all pictures of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:16.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We've been together since we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you remember how I confessed my feelings for you in first grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You said you liked me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You said you loved me and asked me to be your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We were just acting for our Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're embellishing facts to suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:34.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was when I decided to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've told you over and over,\NI don't intend to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:40.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Listen, Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:42.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We've never even dated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:46.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We played together when we were little,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but we're not kids anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:52.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I like Mister Giraffe, I like Mister Elephant, and I like Kouko-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm past the age of saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:01.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Our relationship is destined, eternal, and absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sick of your assumptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's a girl I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You met her on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:16.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oka Chinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:23.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you bother Chinami again,\NI'll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:25.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:28.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Am I not special?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:40.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who cheered you up when you cried because you didn't win a gold medal in calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:45.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who baked you a cake to congratulate you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,when you were chosen to run in the relay race at the sports festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was chosen to be the anchor for the girls, and we took first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:58.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I ran faster than everyone else because I thought you were watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and I could hear you cheering for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:05.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The reason I can run fast, the reason I want to be beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and the one I want to love... It's all you, Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I should be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:15.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why I tried so hard to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:21.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So why... am I not special?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Am I not important to you at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You've never tried to understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were always about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why you don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Of course you are important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why I can't date you just for the sake of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:45.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're special, but you can't be my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't think of you as my soul mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:53.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if I dated you out of pity,\NI don't think it would make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I'm important...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I'm special, how is that different from loving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can't that be part of loving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:09.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...fall in love with me and marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is it because of everything I've done to make you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:18.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do all our memories count for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:23.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't need you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Forget everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Act like it never happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:33.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If there's no fixing it, just forget everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:48.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:49.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:58.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The old Tada Banri disappeared from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's okay, Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:03.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's really okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, we should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:25.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:30.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm performing in that concert tonight at nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you're going to die, die by music.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:36.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm NANA.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? NANA?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, are you really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I can't be perfect, I'm better off falling apart completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:54.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't need to come with me, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:15:59.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm falling apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:26.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo's a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:40.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:53.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This stage is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:01.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This room is filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:11.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You heard what Mitsuo said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:20.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He won't date me because it wouldn't make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When he said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:29.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I realized I've never thought about Mitsuo's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:33.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've just been telling him\NI love him and pursuing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just wanted to do things according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:42.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If the person you love doesn't love you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,you're worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's what I told myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:51.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I only insisted Mitsuo love me, accept me, and not reject me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,because I was forcing that conviction on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Took me long enough to notice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think everyone's like that to some extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really? Even you, Tada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:10.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Accepting the new me that everyone rejects is really difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:14.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I mean, my amnesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:19.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When I'm with my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:27.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're waiting for the old me, the real Tada Banri, to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:34.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The personality that disappeared might simply come back one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If that happens, my current self will vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But that would make everyone happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I stay the way I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,everyone will continue to be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:47.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:50.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:55.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll never be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After all, if you disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:03.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,who am I supposed to share my disgraceful self with tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's only you, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So don't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:13.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know I'm an idiot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:20.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Because... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I like you, Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:36.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I like you, Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:43.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But, it's not fair for me to confess to you now, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't ask you to forget, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:51.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:52.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,T-tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-what's happening tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:58.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We left our bags in a locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,O-our bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:05.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're always running away without our bags, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:08.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I actually enjoy it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:16.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It seems everything turns out fine no matter what I leave behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I seem to be surprisingly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:23.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You know, I lost my shoes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:31.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:31.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you know the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:33.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Should I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, I'll be fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:39.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't want you to see how I look now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:40.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can use my sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks.
